DTSTAMP:20260620T145539Z
DTSTART:20260626T193000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a fun afternoon of painting your pet’s portrait whi
	le sipping on a delicious selection at the Eureka Heights! \n🐾PET PORTRAIT
	 SIP & DESIGN! 🐾 \nCalling all pet lovers and art enthusiasts! Join us for
	 the most adorable creative event at @eurekaheights! \n🎨 What’s Included:\
	n• All painting materials\n• Guided pet portrait session\n• Tons of fun! \
	nPlease send a picture of your pet after signing up or bring your favorite
	 four-legged friend (in photo form) and create a masterpiece you’ll treasu
	re forever! No painting experience is necessary – just bring your creativi
	ty and be ready to have fun!\nEvent Link\n\nhttps://www.eurekaheights.com/
	event/pet-portrait-sip-design-at-eureka-heights-2026-06-26/\n\nFrom Eureka
	 Heights Brewery
